 表示，由于这些复杂因素及其对整个生态系统潜在的影响，OpenAI 表示将谨慎推进文本溯源技术的研究，并优先考虑视听内容的认证工具。OpenAI 承认正研发 ChatGPT 文本水印，但面临挑战"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-097b228b55bad0660d9e5912fb43bb92_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663490283"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivb+Z4LCn1LMNEAMaCTEwOTcyMDA4MSCC98C1BjAAOGJAGXIJNjYzNDkwMjgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1722928743.830978", "card_id": "Q_663232300", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 57}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "新能源汽车为什么要取消传统仪表盘？这样做的目的是什么？对安全性有什么影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8e0666fbfa60b43b7a67f59f39ac24c8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663232300"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivb+Z4LCn1LMNEAMaCTEwOTY2MjYzNCDDn7C1BjAAOFZAGnIJNjYzMjMyMzAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1722928743.831227", "card_id": "Q_663503957", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 91}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《崩坏星穹铁道》8.5 末日剧场支配恶兽？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "个人感觉相比上一期难不少"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f5443f65c08cabea43eded3b0ab89d43_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663503957"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivb+Z4LCn1LMNEAMaCTEwOTcyMzEyMSDw5cG1BjAAOFdAG3IJNjYzNTAzOTU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_typ